  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >When an intergalactic thief robs the arcane Power Crystals, it’s up to Cardinal, Azura, Banana and Pistachio to work together as one being to save the day! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1264520/extras/4e51a6517c27b8ce786507b114897c82.poster.avif?t=1773260084\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1264520/extras/4e51a6517c27b8ce786507b114897c82.webm?t=1773260084\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1264520/extras/4e51a6517c27b8ce786507b114897c82.mp4?t=1773260084\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >As you run, jump, and slide your way through colorful levels, you’ll have to combine each character’s unique abilities to traverse the challenging terrain in your way! Clear wide pits by double jumping as Cardinal, then swap to Azura to dash across, or climb up a wall as Banana, then gracefully glide over the abyss as Pistachio.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1264520/extras/52d051cf9c9905967ed3aad3770eccd0.poster.avif?t=1773260084\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1264520/extras/52d051cf9c9905967ed3aad3770eccd0.webm?t=1773260084\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1264520/extras/52d051cf9c9905967ed3aad3770eccd0.mp4?t=1773260084\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Key Features:</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 3 distinct worlds chock-full of mystery and adventure!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Responsive controls with room for skillful mastery!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > A wonderful and vibrant hand-drawn pixel-art aesthetic!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Hectic boss-fights against larger-than-life creatures!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Deep and fluid moveset!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > A charming cast of quirky characters!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > An upbeat soundtrack composed by Christoph Jakob!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Assist Mode options!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > …vehicles and guns?</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1264520/extras/0097b29249c2e2c03b7e487e326fd1bd.poster.avif?t=1773260084\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1264520/extras/0097b29249c2e2c03b7e487e326fd1bd.webm?t=1773260084\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1264520/extras/0097b29249c2e2c03b7e487e326fd1bd.mp4?t=1773260084\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Unleash Your Creativity!</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Create the levels of your dreams using the <strong>Level Builder</strong>, and upload even your wildest creations to the <strong>Steam Workshop</strong>! There are hundreds of user-generated levels ready to download and play, so there's always something new waiting for you.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1264520/extras/afa1149158ad1fd0b40515ee509fd633.poster.avif?t=1773260084\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1264520/extras/afa1149158ad1fd0b40515ee509fd633.webm?t=1773260084\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1264520/extras/afa1149158ad1fd0b40515ee509fd633.mp4?t=1773260084\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >If that’s not enough, you can even create and share your own pets using the <strong>Pet Maker</strong> - they’ll follow you around in levels and explore the world with you!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1264520/extras/79f4d012a003434badd13db8b2edc32d.poster.avif?t=1773260084\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1264520/extras/79f4d012a003434badd13db8b2edc32d.webm?t=1773260084\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1264520/extras/79f4d012a003434badd13db8b2edc32d.mp4?t=1773260084\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Vibrant Venture is currently in Early Access, delivering a nearly complete gameplay experience. As development progresses, some elements may evolve based on feedback and refinement. We’re excited to have you along for the journey!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >When an intergalactic thief robs the arcane Power Crystals, it’s up to Cardinal, Azura, Banana and Pistachio to work together as one being to save the day! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1264520/extras/4e51a6517c27b8ce786507b114897c82.poster.avif?t=1773260084\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1264520/extras/4e51a6517c27b8ce786507b114897c82.webm?t=1773260084\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1264520/extras/4e51a6517c27b8ce786507b114897c82.mp4?t=1773260084\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >As you run, jump, and slide your way through colorful levels, you’ll have to combine each character’s unique abilities to traverse the challenging terrain in your way! Clear wide pits by double jumping as Cardinal, then swap to Azura to dash across, or climb up a wall as Banana, then gracefully glide over the abyss as Pistachio.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1264520/extras/52d051cf9c9905967ed3aad3770eccd0.poster.avif?t=1773260084\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1264520/extras/52d051cf9c9905967ed3aad3770eccd0.webm?t=1773260084\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1264520/extras/52d051cf9c9905967ed3aad3770eccd0.mp4?t=1773260084\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Key Features:</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 3 distinct worlds chock-full of mystery and adventure!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Responsive controls with room for skillful mastery!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > A wonderful and vibrant hand-drawn pixel-art aesthetic!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Hectic boss-fights against larger-than-life creatures!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Deep and fluid moveset!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > A charming cast of quirky characters!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > An upbeat soundtrack composed by Christoph Jakob!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Assist Mode options!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > …vehicles and guns?</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1264520/extras/0097b29249c2e2c03b7e487e326fd1bd.poster.avif?t=1773260084\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1264520/extras/0097b29249c2e2c03b7e487e326fd1bd.webm?t=1773260084\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1264520/extras/0097b29249c2e2c03b7e487e326fd1bd.mp4?t=1773260084\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Unleash Your Creativity!</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Create the levels of your dreams using the <strong>Level Builder</strong>, and upload even your wildest creations to the <strong>Steam Workshop</strong>! There are hundreds of user-generated levels ready to download and play, so there's always something new waiting for you.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1264520/extras/afa1149158ad1fd0b40515ee509fd633.poster.avif?t=1773260084\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1264520/extras/afa1149158ad1fd0b40515ee509fd633.webm?t=1773260084\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1264520/extras/afa1149158ad1fd0b40515ee509fd633.mp4?t=1773260084\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >If that’s not enough, you can even create and share your own pets using the <strong>Pet Maker</strong> - they’ll follow you around in levels and explore the world with you!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1264520/extras/79f4d012a003434badd13db8b2edc32d.poster.avif?t=1773260084\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1264520/extras/79f4d012a003434badd13db8b2edc32d.webm?t=1773260084\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1264520/extras/79f4d012a003434badd13db8b2edc32d.mp4?t=1773260084\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Vibrant Venture is currently in Early Access, delivering a nearly complete gameplay experience. As development progresses, some elements may evolve based on feedback and refinement. We’re excited to have you along for the journey!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
